df.pivot_table(valus = '', index = '', columns = '', fill_value = '', aggfunc = [] , margins = True/False)

values: values want to check
index: group by
columns: second group by 
fill_value: make all missing value(NaN) as 0
aggfunc: apply functions such as np.median, np.mean
margins: Count for each column, mean for each row by default
